collectionMetadata.name: Filing of Tax Returns, Annual
collectionMetadata.description: Number of returns issued, received, and received on time for Individual Income Tax and Corporate Income Tax (for Year of Assessment (YA)2006 to YA2022), and Goods and Services Tax (for Financial Year (FY)2006 to FY2022).

datasetMetadata.name: Filing of Tax Returns for Goods and Services Tax
Filing of Tax Returns for Individual Income Tax and Corporate Income Tax
datasetMetadata.description:
* No-Filing Service refers to individuals who received No-Filing Service letters and did not need to make any changes to their tax returns.
* The figures for Individual Income Tax and Corporate Income Tax returns are as at 31 March of the following year for each Year of Assessment (i.e. the YA2016 figures are as at 31 March 2017).
* The figures for Internet Filing, Telephone Filing and No-Filing Service are as at 18 April of each year. Telephone Filing is no longer available with effect from Year of Assessment 2010.
* For Year of Assessment 2020, the figures for Internet Filing and No-Filing Service are as at 31 May 2020 as filing extension was granted.
